          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/34346836-life-the-universe-and-everything">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/40481325-bernardo?shelf=humour">humour</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/40481325-bernardo?shelf=science-fiction">science-fiction</a>
